node.text:
Sometimes it takes a dose of adrenaline to remind the body that it’s alive, to actually be moved by an experience to the point of goosebumps. Today’s shock to the system came by way of the @mvagustausa #turismovelocelusso 420lbs of pure twisted steal and sex appeal. An incredibly well balanced combination of Italian styling , Herculean strength, and Prima Ballerina handling. The higher handlebar mount makes this a perfect choice for destination rides to get away, or carving twisty pavement into giggles of “holy shit that was an awesome turn” feelings. This bike turned heads and dropped jaws everywhere I rode it. Don’t even get me started on the throaty exhaust notes out of the trio of pipes! It’s nothing less than an Italian combustion opera, it’s like riding a motorcycle with its own badass theme song! 
Regardless of what you ride, be safe out there. Get training, get proper gear, and have at it! 🏍

Suited and Booted by:
#alpinestars #alpinestarsboots  Head protection by:
#bellracestar 
@mvagustamotor #MotorcycleArt  #sena30k 
📸 @heaththechief

node.text: After a few moments to reflect on how blessed I am for being the son of Paul Ziering, I spent the day being the dad that that man raised  this man to be. Happy Father’s Day to you all 🙏

node.text: There’s really nothing better than spending quality time with my kids. Penna became so good at Paddle boarding I let her take me for a spin! Mia spent the entire weekend in the kayak! I spent the entire weekend feeling blessed.  It’s with a heartfelt thanks to all the people in our armed forces who gave the ultimate sacrifice so America can remain the land of the free. 🙏 #memorialdayweekend
